RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTBS_ROLL_MARGIN_DETAILS.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.VERSION_NO = LBTBS_ROLL_MARGIN_DETAILS.VERSION_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.SPLIT_NO = LBTBS_ROLL_MARGIN_DETAILS.SPLIT_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.COMPONENT = LBTBS_ROLL_MARGIN_DETAILS.COMPONENT

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.Product_Code, b.Product_Description FROM Lbtbs_Borrower_Drawdown_Prod a, Oltms_Product b, Oltms_Product_Master_Ld c WHERE a.Product_Code = b.Product_Code AND a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND b.Product_Code = c.Product AND c.Participant_Product IS NOT NULL AND a.Version_No = (SELECT MAX(Version_No) FROM Lbtbs_Borrower_Drawdown_Prod WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ?) UNION SELECT a.Dd_Product_Code, b.Product_Description FROM Lbtbs_Contract_Borr_Ddprod a, Oltms_Product b, Oltms_Product_Master_Ld c WHERE a.Dd_Product_Code = b.Product_Code AND a.Contract_Ref_No = ? AND a.Version_No = (SELECT Latest_Version_No FROM Oltbs_Contract WHERE Contract_Ref_No = ?) AND a.Customer_No = ? AND b.Product_Code = c.Product AND c.Participant_Product IS NOT NULL AND b.Product_Code = c.Product AND c.Participant_Product IS NOT NULL

SELECT DISTINCT a.Rate_Code, a.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE a,Cftms_Float_Rate_Master b WHERE a.Rate_Code = b.Rate_Code AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND b.Ccy_Code = ? AND b.Branch_Code = Global.Current_Branch UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE) ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT Rate_Code FROM (SELECT Rate_Code FROM Lftms_Standard_Rate_Code WHERE Rate_Type = 'S' AND Record_Stat = 'O' AND Auth_Stat = 'A' AND NVL(?,'S') IN ('S','U') UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT a.Rate_Code FROM Lftms_Treasury_Rate_Code a,Oltms_Static_Maintenance b WHERE a.Rate_Code = b.Field_Name AND a.Auth_Stat = 'A' AND a.Record_Stat = 'O' AND b.Maintenance_Type = 'RTCD' AND a.Rate_Code_Usage = b.Field_Type AND 'T' = NVL(?,'S')) WHERE 'X' = ?

SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND A.RATE_CODE_USAGE = B.FIELD_TYPE UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR AS RATE_CODE_DESC, A.AUTH_STAT AS AUTH_STAT, A.RECORD_STAT AS RECORD_STAT FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC, AUTH_STAT, RECORD_STAT FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S') WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE

SELECT a.Frequency, a.Rate_Code, a.Units,a.Ccy_Code FROM Lftm_Tenor_Code_Maint a,Lftm_Rate_Code_Maint b WHERE a.Rate_Code = ? AND a.Ccy_Code = ? AND a.Rate_Code = b.Rate_Code AND a.Ccy_Code = b.Ccy_Code AND b.Auth_Stat = 'A'
